dcterms:description: A bibliographic network in computer science, which includes papers, authors, venues, and terms as four types of vertices. It is used for similarity search among authors based on various meta-paths.
dcterms:title: DBLP

dcterms:description: A social media network of Yelp, which includes businesses, words in business names, reviews of businesses, and words in reviews as vertices. It is used for similarity search among businesses based on user-defined meta-paths.
dcterms:title: Yelp
